detailedDescription.articleBody: Jacqueline Tong is an English actress who is best known for playing Daisy Barnes in the period drama Upstairs, Downstairs from 1973 to 1975. In 1975, she was nominated for Outstanding Supporting Actress in a Drama Series in the Primetime Emmy Awards. In 1982 she appeared in Coronation Street, babysitting for Gail's son Nicky.
